Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是只有人質 沒有其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.42,0:19:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎的確是安全
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我現在就去你們那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:16.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事麼?把機體留下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.42,0:19:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.01,0:19:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}IFF 敵我自動識別系統
