Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.71,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Topaz 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀Mark-II 切換到搜敵模式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 還真古怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:45.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.39,0:19:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點反擊都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說對方是個舊型的Salvage 也不會多厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.69,0:19:54.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起綁架時的那些高技巧的行動來說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在打倒的Salvage 太單調了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宗介也這樣認為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.39,0:20:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯　沒有看到敵人的步兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.79,0:20:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可疑啊 把要檢查的東西檢查完後 就趕快撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 已經沒問題了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不是什麼化學武器的…圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空調也有在動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂　這果然是很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.39,0:20:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼　怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊毀的敵機沒有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.39,0:20:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無人的!　也就是說是遠距離操作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uruz6　剛才的我沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.90,0:20:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.90,0:20:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫魯茲 他怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.80,0:21:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:14.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信線路很差　而且沒有任何回音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.20,0:21:16.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 等一下 可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連通了!
